  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX spot at 6607.16 sitting just below the GEX flip at 6607 and massive positive gamma wall at 6610 (+69.3B), dealers are currently in equilibrium but will aggressively sell any push toward 6610 to hedge their long gamma positions. The PIN regime with heavy positive GEX concentration between 6605-6625 creates a strong magnetic effect that should contain price action within this range, with dealers providing natural resistance on rallies and support on dips. Key levels: watch for dealer selling pressure into 6610-6615 and buying support if we test back toward 6605 or the negative gamma pocket at 6590.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect the market to get pinned between 6605-6615 with limited breakout potential.",
